<div class="title">Altered Existence</div>
<div class="substance">Ayahuasca</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Sephalon&Exact=1">Sephalon</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Sephalon. "Altered Existence: An Experience with Ayahuasca (exp52327)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. May 4, 2006. erowid.org/exp/52327</div>

<br/>



